<div class="about-page">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <div class="about-hero">
    <div class="about-hero__glow"></div>
    <div class="about-hero__inner">
      <div class="about-eyebrow-pill">Our Story</div>
      <h1 class="about-hero__headline">Born in Northern California.<br>Built for how you actually live.</h1>
      <p class="about-hero__sub">We didn't start a mushroom company. We started looking for something better — and when we couldn't find it, we built it.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Origin story -->
  <section class="about-origin">
    <div class="about-origin__inner">
      <div class="about-section-eyebrow">The Origin</div>
      <h2 class="about-section-title">Why Happie exists</h2>
      <div class="about-origin__prose">
        <p>The energy drink market is a paradox. Products engineered to make you feel good — packed with synthetic stimulants, artificial colors, and enough sugar to spike your cortisol before your morning meeting even starts. We used them anyway, because the alternative was nothing.</p>
        <p>Meanwhile, functional mushrooms had decades of legitimate science behind them. Lion's Mane studied for cognitive support. Cordyceps used by Olympic athletes. Reishi prescribed in traditional medicine for immune balance and stress. All of it locked away in capsules that tasted like dirt and required remembering to take them.</p>
        <p class="about-origin__key-quote">Happie Fungi Fusion started with a simple question: <strong>What if the thing you reached for tasted incredible and actually did something?</strong></p>
        <p>Two years of formulation. Dozens of flavor iterations. A commitment to fruiting body extracts, dual-extraction, and third-party testing on every batch. The result is a drink we're proud of — and one that's earned the trust of 1,200+ verified buyers who've made it part of their daily routine.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="about-values">
    <div class="about-values__inner">
      <div class="about-section-eyebrow">What We Stand For</div>
      <h2 class="about-section-title about-section-title--left">Our commitments</h2>
      <div class="about-values__grid">

        <div class="about-value-card">
          <span class="about-value-card__num">01</span>
          <div class="about-value-card__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M14 3C14 3 8 7 8 14a6 6 0 0012 0C20 7 14 3 14 3z" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none"/>
              <line x1="14" y1="14" x2="14" y2="25" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <line x1="10" y1="22" x2="18" y2="22" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <circle cx="14" cy="11" r="1.5" fill="#2D6A4F"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="about-value-card__title">Radical Transparency</h3>
          <p class="about-value-card__body">Every batch is third-party tested and QR-coded to the full lab report. You know exactly what's in your can — potency, purity, contaminants. No exceptions.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-value-card">
          <span class="about-value-card__num">02</span>
          <div class="about-value-card__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M14 4 C14 4 10 8 10 13 C10 16.31 11.79 19.2 14 20.5 C16.21 19.2 18 16.31 18 13 C18 8 14 4 14 4z" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none"/>
              <path d="M14 20.5 L14 26" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <path d="M10 24 L18 24" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <path d="M7 14 C7 14 4 12 4 9" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <path d="M21 14 C21 14 24 12 24 9" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="about-value-card__title">Real Ingredients Only</h3>
          <p class="about-value-card__body">No artificial flavors, no synthetic vitamins, no shortcuts. Fruiting body mushroom extracts, organic agave, and natural flavors. The label says what it means.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-value-card">
          <span class="about-value-card__num">03</span>
          <div class="about-value-card__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <line x1="14" y1="3" x2="14" y2="25" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <line x1="6" y1="7" x2="22" y2="7" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <path d="M6 7 L4 14 C4 17.31 6.69 20 10 20 L10 20 C13.31 20 16 17.31 16 14 L14 7" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none"/>
              <path d="M22 7 L24 14 C24 17.31 21.31 20 18 20" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="about-value-card__title">Effective Doses</h3>
          <p class="about-value-card__body">2,000mg per can — formulated to match doses used in clinical research. Not trace amounts for label claims. Actual amounts that move the needle.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-value-card">
          <span class="about-value-card__num">04</span>
          <div class="about-value-card__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <circle cx="14" cy="14" r="10" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width="1.8" fill="none"/>
              <line x1="8" y1="8" x2="20" y2="20" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="about-value-card__title">No Alcohol. Ever.</h3>
          <p class="about-value-card__body">We built something you can drink at any time of day, in any setting, at any age. Clean energy that doesn't compromise your clarity or your character.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-value-card">
          <span class="about-value-card__num">05</span>
          <div class="about-value-card__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <circle cx="14" cy="14" r="10" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width="1.8" fill="none"/>
              <path d="M4 14 Q9 10 14 14 Q19 18 24 14" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" fill="none"/>
              <line x1="14" y1="4" x2="14" y2="24" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="about-value-card__title">Sustainable Sourcing</h3>
          <p class="about-value-card__body">Our mushrooms are cultivated — not wild-harvested — using sustainable agricultural practices. Ocean-derived minerals sourced responsibly. Packaging designed to minimize waste.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-value-card">
          <span class="about-value-card__num">06</span>
          <div class="about-value-card__icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M14 23 C14 23 4 17 4 10 C4 7.24 6.24 5 9 5 C11.04 5 12.81 6.19 13.72 7.93 C13.86 8.21 14.14 8.21 14.28 7.93 C15.19 6.19 16.96 5 19 5 C21.76 5 24 7.24 24 10 C24 17 14 23 14 23z" stroke="#2D6A4F" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="about-value-card__title">Community First</h3>
          <p class="about-value-card__body">1,200+ verified reviews. Real people. Real results. We read every piece of feedback and iterate constantly. Happie exists because of the people who believed in it early.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats bar -->
  <section class="about-stats">
    <div class="about-stats__inner">
      <div class="about-section-eyebrow about-section-eyebrow--light">By the Numbers</div>
      <h2 class="about-stats__headline">What 2 years of work looks like</h2>
      <div class="about-stats__grid">
        <div class="about-stat-card">
          <div class="about-stat-card__num">1,200+</div>
          <div class="about-stat-card__label">Happie customers</div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stat-card">
          <div class="about-stat-card__num">4.9</div>
          <div class="about-stat-card__label">Average rating</div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stat-card">
          <div class="about-stat-card__num">40+</div>
          <div class="about-stat-card__label">States shipping to</div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stat-card">
          <div class="about-stat-card__num">100%</div>
          <div class="about-stat-card__label">Lab verified batches</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="about-cta">
    <div class="about-cta__inner">
      <h2 class="about-cta__headline">Taste the difference.</h2>
      <p class="about-cta__sub">Start with any flavor. You'll understand in one can.</p>
      <a href="/collections/all" class="btn-primary btn-lg">Shop Now &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</div>

